Orbit RV Park, owned and operated by Orbit RV Park, Inc., offers RVers a very pleasant refuge from Northern Winters and provides these amenities for our guests:
30 and 50 amp service
water & sewer connections
free wi-fi is available throughout most of the Park
free courtesy phone available in the Clubhouse
free coffee every morning in our Clubhouse (tea selection & hot water all day)
fishing dock that extends 125’ into the Indian River
sites for rigs up to 40’
grassy sites, with block patios and picnic tables
some pull-through spaces
coin laundry open 24 hours (quarters available in Office)
free showers
exercise room
snip fresh herbs for dinner from Orbit’s herb garden (availability varies)
small pets permitted, with restrictions
a comfortable Clubhouse
friendly and helpful resident managers
easy driving distance to Florida’s most popular attractions
excellent local restaurants (inquire at the Office)
convenient to shopping and RV suppliers (inquire at Office for directions)
overlooks the Indian River
close to TWO public boat launches (Orbit has storage space
available for your boat)
regular
activities
full of nice, friendly folks!
One of our special Activities is our Friday Cooking Demo! At 2:00 every Friday, Orbit RV Park Staff demonstrates how to cook a tasty dish! Every week, it’s something different. In addition to tasting the recipe results, we always taste a different cheese and a different wine. (Remember, at Orbit, something tasty is always going on!) Click here for a list of the
